data.title: 2024 Best Of Tomah Wisconsin
data.meta_description: Best of Tomah Wisconsin is a survey that celebrates the businesses, places, and people in Tomah, WI. Presented by the Tomah Chamber.
data.meta_site_name: Greater Tomah Area Chamber of Commerce / CVB
data.text:
WINNERS OF THE 2024 BEST OF TOMAH SURVEY!

In January of 2024, the Tomah Chamber and Visitors Center launched the 2024 Best of Tomah, WI survey. Locals and visitors were invited to nominate and celebrate the excellence within Tomah, Wisconsin. The survey ran from January 15th to March 4th, and survey participants had the opportunity to cast their votes for the "2024 Best Of Tomah, WI" across various categories.

The survey created a lot of local and regional buzz, with the first round of voting generating 1,700 survey submissions and the second round almost tripling that number with 4,900 survey submissions.Â The results of the survey are below.Â
